## 🚨 Common Issues & Solutions

### Foreign Key Errors
```bash
# Error: "Key is not present in table X"
# Fix: Check types.ts Relationships array
# Use correct referenced table IDs
```

### Build Failures
```bash
npm run lint:fix  # Auto-fix linting
npm run build     # Retry build
```

### RLS Blocks
- Check user clinic context
- Verify clinic_id in queries
- Test with different user roles

